@Ollie wrote:

JaGeX know they will never be able to stop cheating, so they are just kicking you in the teeth saying “haha you have wasted x hours, have fun at level 3”

item.title: Quintuplets
item.dc:creator: @Rixxx Rix_
item.description:
@Rixxx wrote:

BloodRayne:

Holy shit. Check their adventurers logs, lmfao. When I posted this they all had att/str ranked. Fuck. This whole roll back system is getting abused so hard… They’re now all epic tank accounts…

Ooo, Jagex roll-backed all accounts in 3 minutes, that’s fast. :eek: Anyway, this roll-back system is stupid, when someone gets their stats rolled back, the bot will probably continue to run and earn those levels back. However if an account gets banned, then the bot stops and a new account has to be made. :rolleyes:
